{"id": "art-281", "label": "Art. 281", "title": "Art. 281: Nulităţile absolute", "slug": "art-281", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 281: Nulit&#259;&#355;ile absolute </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'>Determin&#259; întotdeauna aplicarea nulit&#259;&#355;ii\nînc&#259;lcarea dispozi&#355;iilor privind:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>a)<b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>compunerea completului de judecat&#259;;</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_808069497\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1989\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_808069497\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>*) Admite excep&#355;ia de neconstitu&#355;ionalitate\nridicat&#259; de Elena Ilie în Dosarul nr. 2.223/192/2016 al Judec&#259;toriei\nBolintin-Vale &#351;i constat&#259; c&#259; dispozi&#355;iile art. 281 alin.\n(4) lit. a) din </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>Codul de procedur&#259;\npenal&#259;</span><span style='color:black'> raportat la art. 281 alin. (1)\nlit. f) din acela&#351;i act normativ sunt neconstitu&#355;ionale.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1804786394\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1988\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1804786394\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>Definitiv&#259; &#351;i general obligatorie.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>b)<b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>competen&#355;a material&#259; &#351;i\ncompeten&#355;a personal&#259; a instan&#355;elor judec&#259;tore&#351;ti,\natunci când judecata a fost efectuat&#259; de o instan&#355;&#259;\ninferioar&#259; celei legal competente;</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2043976242\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1987\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2043976242\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>*) Curtea Constitu&#355;ional&#259; admite excep&#355;ia de\nneconstitu&#355;ionalitate &#351;i constat&#259; c&#259; solu&#355;ia\nlegislativ&#259; cuprins&#259; în dispozi&#355;iile art. 281 alin. (1) lit. b),\ncare nu reglementeaz&#259; în categoria nulit&#259;&#355;ilor absolute\nînc&#259;lcarea dispozi&#355;iilor referitoare la competen&#355;a\nmaterial&#259; &#351;i dup&#259; calitatea persoanei a organului de\nurm&#259;rire penal&#259;, este neconstitu&#355;ional&#259;.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1819931039\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1986\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1819931039\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b<sup>1</sup>)competen&#355;a material&#259; &#351;i\ncompeten&#355;a dup&#259; calitatea persoanei a organului de urm&#259;rire\npenal&#259;;</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>c)publicitatea\n&#351;edin&#355;ei de judecat&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>d)participarea\nprocurorului, atunci când participarea sa este obligatorie potrivit legii;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>e)prezen&#355;a\nsuspectului sau a inculpatului, atunci când participarea sa este obligatorie\npotrivit legii;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1684611930\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1985\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1684611930\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>f)asistarea de c&#259;tre avocat a suspectului &#351;i a\npersoanei v&#259;t&#259;mate, respectiv a inculpatului &#351;i a celorlalte\np&#259;r&#355;i, atunci când asisten&#355;a este obligatorie.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)Nulitatea absolut&#259; se\nconstat&#259; din oficiu sau la cerere.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_24236677\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1984\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_24236677\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Înc&#259;lcarea dispozi&#355;iilor legale prev&#259;zute\nla alin. (1) lit. a), b), c) &#351;i d) poate fi invocat&#259; în orice stare a\nprocesului.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_347462822\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1983\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_347462822\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Înc&#259;lcarea\ndispozi&#355;iilor legale prev&#259;zute la alin. (1) lit. b<sup>1</sup>), e)\n&#351;i f) poate fi invocat&#259;:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1871308458\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1982\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1871308458\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)pân&#259; la încheierea procedurii în camera\npreliminar&#259;, dac&#259; înc&#259;lcarea a intervenit în cursul\nurm&#259;ririi penale;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_784965129\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1981\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_784965129\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)în orice stare a procesului, dac&#259; înc&#259;lcarea a\nintervenit în procedura camerei preliminare sau în cursul judec&#259;&#355;ii;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2119774572\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1980\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2119774572\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)în orice stare a procesului, indiferent de momentul la\ncare a intervenit înc&#259;lcarea, când instan&#355;a a fost sesizat&#259; cu\nun acord de recunoa&#351;tere a vinov&#259;&#355;iei.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}